citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:55pm on January
17, 2023. No one answered to a knock on the facility door. A voicemail message was left and a text sent. Licensee
responded to the text stating licensee was not available for an inspection today.
End Section
